      == Usage questions

      Our friendly volunteer community answers OptaPlanner questions on StackOverflow.

      To get a helpful answer, follow https://stackoverflow.com/help/how-to-ask[the StackOverflow guidelines] such as:

      * Get to the point. Keep it short.
      * Be crystal clear. Reread your question before posting it.
      * Add relevant technical details: stacktrace, code snippet, ...

    .text-center<
      %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-success.versionedButton(href="https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/optaplanner")<
        %img(src="question.png" alt="Question")
        %div
          %span Ask/view StackOverflow questions
      .small
        Opinionated questions aren't welcome on StackOverflow,
        %br
        so those belong on our discussion forum below.

    %div(style="margin-top: 20px")
      :asciidoc
        There's also a real-time chat: use an IRC client (such as https://hexchat.github.io/[HexChat])
        to connect to http://freenode.net/[a freenode server] (such as `chat.freenode.net`)
        and join the channels `#optaplanner` and `#drools`.

