          == Support (paid)

          For a fast, enterprise quality answer, open a support case with Red Hat.

          Red Hat sponsors this open source project by employing its core developers.
          They have dedicated QA and support teams around this project.

        .text-center<
          %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-primary.versionedButton(href="https://access.redhat.com/support/cases/#/case/new")<
            %img(src="question.png" alt="Question")
            %div
              %span Open a support case
          .small
            :asciidoc
              This requires link:../product/services.html[a support subscription].

