      == Contribution questions

      For change proposals or opinionated discussions, join our discussion forum
      or mail directly through mailto:optaplanner-dev@googlegroups.com[optaplanner-dev@googlegroups.com].

      It's recommended to link:../code/sourceCode.html[build OptaPlanner from source] before starting a discussion here.

    .text-center<
      %a.btn.btn-lg.btn-info.versionedButton(href="https://groups.google.com/forum/#!forum/optaplanner-dev")<
        %div
          %span Start/view discussions on our forum
      .small
        Please don't cross post to both our forum and StackOverflow.

    %div(style="margin-top: 20px")
      :asciidoc
        If you're working on a contribution, come talk to us on Freenode in the channel `#optaplanner-dev`.
        The core developers are there during working hours (depending on their timezone).

